Description: A perforated cylinder seal: of dark green serpentine, bearing an incised inscription. Good condition, although the surface of the seal is slightly worn.
Curator's comments: Bibliography: P. Kaplony, 'Die Inschriften der Ägyptischen Frühzeit III (Wiesbaden, 1964), pl. 99, abb. 418; P. Kaplony, 'Die Inschriften der Ägyptischen Frühzeit II (Wiesbaden, 1964), 1149.
